-disease-risk-study-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emuscle-building%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%20pay%20dividends%20for%20long-term%20health%20and%20offer%20an%20immediate%20boost%20to%20energy%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20mood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20super%20happy%20to%20say%20at%20age%20almost%2050%2C%20I%20can%20do%20all%20those%20things%2C%20and%20that%20means%20that%20I%20fear%20very%20little%20during%20any%20given%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20I%20can%20tackle%20these%20hard%20things%20and%20recover%20from%20them.%20So%20whatever%20challenge%20you%20have%2C%20send%20it%20my%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4b5a3c9-2c73-4915-9a8a-88d2635afc6e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESquats%20and%20deadlifts%20'are%20king'%20to%20build%20full-body%20muscle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20Holtan%20hits%20the%20gym%20at%20about%205%3A30%20a.m.%20to%20pump%20iron%20before%20work.%20Her%20routine%20varies%2C%20including%20a%20mix%20of%20strength%20training%2C%20CrossFit%2C%20and%20running%20for%20well-balanced%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-techniques-eccentric-concentric-build-muscle-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emuscle%20and%20strength%20gains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bsquats%20and%20deadlifts%20are%20king%2C%26quot%3B%20Holtan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESquats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20involve%20lowering%20your%20hips%20to%20drop%20your%20butt%20toward%20the%20ground%2C%20then%20returning%20to%20standing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHold%20a%20weight%20(balanced%20on%20your%20back%2C%20in%20front%20of%20your%20chest%2C%20or%20centered%20between%20your%20hands%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-nba-coach-swears-by-goblet-squat-variation-stronger-core-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egoblet%20squat%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20bend%20your%20knees%20