or%20the%20Southeast%20region%20in%20Atlanta%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20Lausanne%20at%20the%20VP%20level%20and%20subsequently%20became%20the%20managing%20director%20for%20multiple%20countries%20in%20Europe%2C%20before%20being%20appointed%20president%20of%20the%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20region.%20I%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20CEO%20of%20PMI's%20US%20business%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Power%20Hours%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20See%20more%20stories%20from%20the%20series%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20celebrated%2030%20years%20at%20PMI.%20I've%20spent%20half%20of%20my%20career%20in%20the%20US%20and%20half%20outside%20the%20US.%20I'm%20a%20former%20smoker%20myself%20who%20switched%20to%20IQOS%2C%20a%20heated%20tobacco%20product%2C%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20day%20in%20my%20life%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22615c7a69-45bb-448e-9445-29f7aeed265b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wake%20up%20between%206%3A30%20a.m.%20and%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20allow%20myself%20five%20minutes%20to%20check%20my%20phone%20and%20ensure%20there's%20nothing%20urgent%2C%20as%20we're%20a%20global%20business%20and%20things%20can%20happen%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20my%20mornings%20with%20a%20mantra%20of%20'pay%20myself%20first.'%20I've%20adopted%20the%20mental%20image%20of%20putting%20my%20own%20oxygen%20mask%20on%20first%2C%20because%20if%20you%20start%20the%20day%20refreshed%2C%20you%20can%20show%20up%20as%20a%20better%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20ideal%20morning%2C%20I%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20take%20a%20mindful%20walk%20in%20my%20neighborhood.%20I%20add%20a%2015-minute%20yoga%20routine%20after%20the%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20less%20ideal%20morning%20is%20when%20I%20skip%20the%20walk%2C%20either%20because%20the%20weather%20isn't%20great%20or%20I%20decide%20to%20trade%20it%20for%2030%20minutes%20of%20extra%20sleep%2C%20and%20then%20try%20to%20get%20my%2015%20minutes%20of%20yoga%20and%20stretching%20to%20start%20the%20day%2C%20regardless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20big%20breakfast%20person%2C%20so%20I%20might%20grab%20a%20handful%20of%20berries%20or%20a%20couple%20of%20figs.%20I%20always%20have%20a%20double%20espresso%20from%20my%20Nespresso%20machine.%20Occasionally%2C%20I'll%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-is-japans-biggest-matcha-buyer-its-straining-the-industry-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ematcha%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20Cuzen%20Matcha%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea0a1034-7b65-4fe3-8ccc-81a3d825fc9c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20hit%20the%20road%20for%20my%20office%20around%208%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20go%20into%20the%20office%20in%20Stamford%20four%20days%20a%20week%20on%20average%2C%20and%20it's%20about%20a%2025-minute%20drive%20away.%20What%20makes%20me%20anxious%20before%20walking%20into%20the%20office%20is%20whether%20the%20business%20is%20moving%20fast%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20if%20we're%20innovating%20with%20urgency%20while%20staying%20disciplined%20and%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mornings%20are%20filled%20with%20meetings.%20I've%20ensured%20we%20have%20a%20well-organized%20office%20layout%20with%20numerous%20open%20spaces%2C%20a%20barista%20bar%2C%20and%20coffee%20corners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20morning