ucks%3C%2Fa%3E%20receives%20more%20than%20a%20million%20job%20applications%20a%20year%2C%20the%20company's%20Chief%20People%20Officer%20says%20one%20reason%20is%20a%20quietly%20powerful%20lure%3A%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20fully-funded%20bachelor's%20degree%20from%20Arizona%20State%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Brea%20Yancey%2C%20a%20barista%20in%20Washington%20state%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20company%20for%20eight%20years%2C%20that%20benefit%20hasn't%20just%20reshaped%20her%20future%20%E2%80%94%20it%20reshaped%20her%20family's.%20She%20enrolled%2C%20then%20inspired%20her%20mother%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-offering-26-weeks-severance-for-managers-at-closing-cafes-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20store%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20join%20her%2C%20turning%20a%20workplace%20perk%20into%20a%20two-generation%20push%20toward%20a%20goal%20neither%20woman%20thought%20was%20financially%20in%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20think%20college%20was%20going%20to%20be%20an%20option%20because%20of%20how%20much%20it%20costs%20with%20loans%20and%20things%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Yancey%2C%20who%20celebrated%20her%20graduation%20on%20Monday%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20all%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20world%20not%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYancey%20pursued%20a%20degree%20in%20interdisciplinary%20arts%20and%20performance%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%20music%20teacher.%20Her%20mother%20graduated%20last%20semester%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20interdisciplinary%20studies%2C%20concentrating%20in%20sales%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20project%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20that%20she%20got%20to%20finish%20school%2C%20because%20that's%20all%20she%20ever%20wanted%2C%20and%20she%20stopped%20originally%20because%20she%20got%20pregnant%20with%20me%2C%20but%20now%20we%20finished%20it%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Yancey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20college%20costs%20have%20soared%2C%20so%20has%20enrollment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-employee-free-college-degree-through-company-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarbucks'%20College%20Achievement%20Plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SCAP)%20program%2C%20Chief%20People%20Officer%20Sara%20Kelly%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20program%2C%20which%20began%20in%202014%2C%20offers%20eligible%20employees%20100%25%20upfront%20tuition%20coverage%20for%20their%20first%20bachelor's%20degree%2C%20facilitated%20through%20online%20classes%20at%20ASU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%2060%25%20increase%20in%20participation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%2013%25%20of%20our%20partners%20participating%20as%20scholars%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20represents%20at%20least%20one%20enrolled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-severance-package-lay-off-staff-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20staff%20member%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20about%2090%25%20of%20its%20coffeehouses%2C%20Kelly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20isn't%20the%20only%20retail%20or%20Fortune%20500%20employer%20offering%20education%20benefits.%20Amazon%2C%20Walmart%2C%20and%20Chipotle%20also%20offer%20similar%20programs.%20However%2C%20compared%20to%20most%20programs%20in%20the%20US%20retail%20sector%2C%20Starbucks%20doesn't%20require%20reimbursement%20of%20tuition%20payments%20or%20require%20students%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20company%20for%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYounger%20students%20are%20increasingly%20questioning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-value-of-college-higher-education-student-debt-tuition-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evalue%20of%20a%20college%20degree%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20May%202024%20Deloitte%20survey%20found%20that%20a%20third%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20chose%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-skipping-college-living-paycheck-to-paycheck-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskip%20higher%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20rising%20costs%2C%20and%20the%20average%20price%20of%20attendance%20for%20a%20student%20living%20on%20campus%20at%20an%20in-state%20public%204-year%20institution%20is%20%24108%2C584%20over%204%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Educationdata%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20you%20can't%20beat%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20started%20over%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20all%20in%20service%20of%20creating%20access%20to%20education%2C%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20creating%20access%20to%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%20%26quot%3BCollege%20is%20incredibly%20costly%2C%20and%20so%20how%20do%20we%20create%20access%20to%20that%20education%20for%20all%20of%20our%20partners%3F%20So%20we're%20really%20proud%2C%20because%20we%20see%20this%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20expressions%20of%20our%20investment%20in%20our%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20has%20expanded%20the%20SCAP%20program%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20offering%20access%20to%20more%20than%20150%20degree%20pathways%2C%20providing%20enrolled%20students%20with%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20fields%20to%20pursue%20than%20in%20the%20program's%20early%20years.%20They've%20also%20added%20a%20%26quot%3BPathway%20to%20Admission%26quot%3B%20support%20route%20for%20partners%20who%20don't%20initially%20qualify%20for%20university%20admission%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20preparatory%20courses%20and%20earn%20their%20way%20into%20ASU.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bplus-one%26quot%3B%20benefit%20is%20available%20for%20eligible%20military%20and%20veteran%20partners%2C%20extending%20SCAP%20to%20a%20qualifying%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Starbucks%20introduced%20new%20study%20abroad%20and%20coffee%20education%20opportunities%2C%20offering%20a%20hands-on%20sustainability%20immersion%20at%20Hacienda%20Alsacia%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourism-is-killing-the-blue-zone-lifestyle-in-costa-rica-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECosta%20Rica%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20scholars%20study%20climate%2C%20agronomy%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20coffee%20at%20their%20global%20research%20and%20development%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20students%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20benefiting.%20The%20program%20is%20a%20significant%20retention%20win%20for%20Starbucks.%20Turnover%20is%20at%20record%20lows%2C%20Kelly%20said%2C%20and%20baristas%20who%20have%20spoken%20to%20Business%20Insider%20frequently%20cite%20the%20SCAP%20program%20as%20a%20reason%20they've%20stayed%20with%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20also%20helps%20to%20strengthen%20Starbucks'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-is-ditching-machines-investing-in-baristas-in-turnaround-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etalent%20pipeline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20company%20has%20committed%20to%20a%2090%25%20internal%20hire%20rate%20or%20fill%20rate%20for%20its%20retail%20leadership%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Starbucks%20college%20achievement%20plan%20partners%20are%20part%20of%20our%20pipeline%20for%20those%20management%20roles%2C%20and%20we're%20very%20excited%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20do%20they%20have%20to%20stay%20with%20Starbucks%3F%20No.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20has%20never%20considered%20adding%20a%20retention%20requirement%20to%20the%20program%2C%20Kelly%20said%2C%20because%20the%20company%20wants%20%26quot%3Bto%20offer%20access%20to%20education%20that%20people%20can%20take%20with%20them%20on%20their%20journey%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20it%20takes%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Yancey%2C%20her%20Starbucks%20journey%20is%20winding%20down%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20over.%20She%20continues%20to%20work%20part-time%20as%20a%20barista%20and%20has%20a%20second%20job%20as%20a%20music%20instructor%2C%20while%20planning%20her%20next%20career%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20whoever%20wants%20to%20go%20into%20the%20university%20through%20the%20SCAP%20program%3B%20they%20find%20a%20way%20for%20you%20to%20complete%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Yancey%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20finances%20or%20learning%20ability%20should%20hold%20anybody%20back%2C%20and%20they%20really%20delivered%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-free-college-program-enrollment-surges-retention-promotions-leadership-pipeline-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766051041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6943347d04eda4732f2dbce2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-free-college-program-enrollment-surges-retention-promotions-leadership-pipeline-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Starbucks'%20Chief%20People%20Officer%20Sara%20Kelly%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20the%20company's%20increasingly%20popular%20free%20college%20program.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-free-college-program-enrollment-surges-retention-promotions-leadership-pipeline-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tony%20responds%20to%20Candy%20Shop%20trolls%20featuring%20Neha%20Kakkar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766050789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-126055559%2Cimgsize-40656.cms%22%2C%22originID%22