%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20aviation%20market%20with%20about%20211%20million%20passengers%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20an%20increase%20of%20about%2011%25%20year-over-year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20global%20airline%20trade%20association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iata.org%2Fen%2Fpressroom%2F2025-releases%2F2025-08-04-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIATA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpiceJet%20said%20it%20will%20help%20Natilus%20navigate%20India's%20regulatory%20process%2C%20with%20the%20order%20contingent%20on%20the%20Horizon%20ultimately%20being%20certified%20in%20the%20country.%20Natilus%20also%20plans%20to%20source%20manufactured%20parts%20from%20India%20and%20has%20established%20a%20subsidiary%20called%20Natilus%20India%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20to%20support%20its%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20publicly%20announced%20international%20airline%20order%20for%20Horizon%2C%20but%20Natilus%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20its%20commercial%20order%20book%20%E2%80%94%20which%20also%20includes%20its%20BWB%20cargo%20version%2C%20Kona%20%E2%80%94%20stands%20at%20more%20than%20570%20orders%20valued%20at%20%2425%20billion%20following%20SpiceJet's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rendering%20of%20the%20horizon%20business%20class%20cabin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6942fa2b832e0ef1ead667c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20the%20proposed%20business%20class%20cabin%20on%20Horizon.%3Cp%3ENatilus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarg-airline-futuristic-blended-wing-body-plane-natlius-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKona%20has%20purchase%20agreements%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarg-airline-futuristic-blended-wing-body-plane-natlius-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20carriers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0like%20US%20operator%20Ameriflight%2C%20a%20partner%20of%20FedEx%2C%20DHL%2C%20and%20UPS%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Canadian%20airline%20Norolinor.%20However%2C%20it's%20unclear%20if%20Horizon%20has%20other%20buyers%20besides%20SpiceJet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22859968e9-2759-4d01-92b1-0519e5ef54cf%5C%22%3EHorizon%20could%20host%20unique%20cabin%20configurations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHorizon%20would%20bring%20a%20new%20type%20of%20aircraft%20to%20India's%20skies%20that%20promises%20better%20operating%20economics%20than%20those%20offered%20by%20the%20reigning%20Boeing-Airbus%20duopoly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatyushev%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Horizon%20will%20offer%20improved%20efficiency%20because%20its%20wing%20design%20generates%20lift%20across%20a%20much%20larger%20surface%20area%2C%20cutting%20fuel%20burn%20by%20roughly%2030%25%20and%20operating%20costs%20by%20about%2050%25%20compared%20with%20similarly%20sized%20aircraft%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-airbus-a320-worlds-most-popular-plane-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoeing%20737%20and%20the%20Airbus%20A320%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rendering%20of%20a%20Natilus%20blended%20wing%20body%20plane%20at%20an%20airport%20gate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717fac9a0a0cc14f22313a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221233%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatilus%20thinks%20its%20blended-wing%20Horizon%20jet%20will%20be%20the%20future%20of%20commercial%20aviation.%3Cp%3ENatilus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%2C%20which%20could%20carry%20up%20to%20240%20people%20in%20a%20high-capacity%20configuration%2C%20would%20also%20fit%20into%20existing%20airport%20infrastructure%20and%20offer%20about%2040%25%20more%20cabin%20space%20thanks%20to%20its%20wider%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatyushev%20said%20this%20could%20translate%20into%20unique%20spaces%20that%20today's%20jets%20can't%20fit%2C%20like%20a%20lounge%20or%20a%20kids'%20playroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenderings%20of%20Horizon%20published%20in%20July%20show%20a%20futuristic%20business%20class%2C%20up%20to%20three%20aisles%20between%20rows%20of%20a%20dozen%20economy%20seats%2C%20and%20dedicated%20privacy%20pods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirbus%20CEO%20Guillaume%20Faury%20recently%20said%20that%20it%20sees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-ceo-said-future-passenger-jets-blended-wing-body-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBWB%20planes%20as%20the%20future%20of%20aviation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20jet%20may%20be%20windowless%20due%20to%20the%20curved%20structure.%20This%20means%20passengers%20could%20face%20minimal%20natural%20light%2C%20disorientation%2C%20and%20claustrophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rendering%20of%20a%20privacy%20pod%20on%20Natilus'%20Horizon%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69388f2e7ecd1d1da6633a18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20above%20rendering%20shows%20Natilus'%20proposed%20%26quot%3Bprivacy%20pods%26quot%3B%20onboard%20the%20wide%20BWB%20jetliner.%3Cp%3ENatilus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wider%20cabin%20also%20poses%20additional%20safety%20challenges%20during%20emergency%20evacuations%20since%20those%20in%20the%20very%20center%20would%20be%20further%20from%20the%20exit%20doors%20than%20on%20today's%20aircraft%2C%20and%20the%20passengers%20and%20crew%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20situation%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatyushev%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Horizon%20would%20have%20windows%2C%20but%20for%20those%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20it%20is%20also%20designing%20skylights%20and%20other%20lighting%20strategies%20to%20mimic%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20previously%20said%20Horizon%20would%20meet%20and%20exceed%20safety%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ba8d67b-ef5b-4114-82bd-fffcf7907774%5C%22%3ECompanies%20have%20long%20experimented%20with%20passenger%20BWBs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BWB%20concept%20is%20not%20new.%20It%20has%20long%20been%20used%20by%20the%20US%20military%20%E2%80%94%20among%20the%20most%20famous%20being%20the%20Northrop%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-us-air-force-is-keeping-b2-spirit-bombers-lethal-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EB-2%20Spirit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stealth%20bomber%20%E2%80%94%20and%20passenger%20variants%20have%20been%20studied%20by%20innovators%20like%20Airbus%2C%20NASA%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20and%20Boeing%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESub-scale%20demonstrators%20have%20flown%2C%20but%20no%20full-sized%20BWB%20has%20been%20certified%20for%20commercial%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20team%20of%20employees%20who%20have%20worked%20for%20companies%20like%20Northrop%20Grumman%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20Natilus%20is%20betting%20Horizon%20can%20break%20into%20the%20fiercely%20competitive%20commercial%20aircraft%20market.%20But%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20player%20chasing%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirbus%20has%20been%20experimenting%20with%20commercial%20BWB%20aircraft%20since%202017%20as%20part%20of%20its%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-new-zero-emission-aircraft-history-of-sustainable-planes-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZEROe%20program%2C%20which%20aims%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20build%20zero-emission%20airliners%20that%C2%A0run%20on%20hydrogen%20instead%20of%20traditional%20jet%20fuel.%20That%20project%20flew%20a%20demonstrator%20in%202019%20but%20has%20since%20been%20delayed%20at%20least%20a%20decade%20from%20its%20initial%2020