com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt-iUvZ-8Q3k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bkiller%20robots%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20cool%20among%20investors%2C%20founders%2C%20and%20tech's%20ascendant%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Luckey%20started%20Anduril%20soon%20after%20leaving%20Meta%2C%20defense%20was%20a%20dirty%20word%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3Binvestors%20would%20advise%20our%20companies%20not%20to%20sell%20to%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Raj%20Shah%2C%20who%20cofounded%20national%20security-focused%20venture%20firm%20Shield%20Capital%2C%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20anymore.%20As%20the%20Trump%20administration%20ramps%20up%20defense%20spending%2C%20as%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20allies%20hustle%20to%20modernize%20warfare%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20foes%20like%20China%2C%20and%20as%20tech's%20elite%20have%20shifted%20to%20the%20right%2C%20defense%20has%20become%2C%20short%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20tech%20industry's%20buzziest%20and%20perhaps%20most%20consequential%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20venture%20fund%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20ravenous%20for%20defense%20tech%2C%20says%20Shah.%20Venture%20capitalists%20sunk%20%2431%20billion%20into%20defense-related%20companies%20in%202024%2C%20up%2033%25%20from%20the%20year%20before%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Findustries%2Faerospace-and-defense%2Four-insights%2Fcreating-a-modernized-defense-technology-frontier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stanford%20students%20whose%20North%20Star%20used%20to%20be%20Google%20are%20now%20vying%20for%20jobs%20at%20Palantir%3B%20some%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-tech-founders-skipping-college-new-dropping-out-palantir-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskipping%20college%20entirely%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20work%20for%20the%20ICE-contracting%20data%20juggernaut.%20Prominent%20tech%20executives%20like%20Meta's%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20and%20OpenAI's%20Kevin%20Weil%20are%20enlisting%20in%20the%20Army%20Reserve.%20And%20factory%20towns%20are%20whirring%20back%20to%20life%3A%20Anduril%2C%20whose%20valuation%20jumped%20from%20%2414%20billion%20in%202024%20to%20more%20than%20%2430%20billion%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20is%20planning%20to%20open%20a%20weapons%20manufacturing%20plant%20outside%20of%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio%2C%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20morphed%20into%20%3Cem%3Eoorah%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20no%20one%20has%20summoned%20that%20vibe%20shift%20quite%20like%20Luckey.%20The%20goateed%2C%20mulleted%2C%20Hawaiian%20shirt-and-cargo-shorts-wearing%2033-year-old%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20never%20served%20in%20the%20military%20%E2%80%94%20has%20become%20the%20foremost%20face%20and%20proselytizer%20of%20tech's%20emphatic%20embrace%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20half-century%2C%20tech%20founders%20have%20reshaped%20how%20humans%20behave%20and%20think.%20Bill%20Gates%20changed%20how%20we%20work.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20changed%20how%20we%20relate%20to%20each%20other.%20Luckey%20is%20changing%20how%20we%20kill.%20And%20he's%20doing%20it%20the%20way%20he%20knows%20best.%20%26quot%3BTake%20me%20with%20a%20pound%20of%20salt%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20told%20Weiss%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20in%20October.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20propagandist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20listening%20to%20hours%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20you%20so%20tour%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20clear%20that%20Luckey's%20cult-of-personality%20campaign%20to%20win%20over%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20a%20bravura%20display%20of%20his%20wily%20business%20acumen%20and%20winking%20weirdness%2C%20has%20three%20rules%3A%20attack%2C%20attack%2C%20attack%3B%20lose%20nothing%2C%20post%20everything%3B%20and%20claim%20victory%2C%20even%20in%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Luckey%20realized%20the%20Defense%20Department%20needed%20a%20rebrand.%20Meservey%2C%20the%20comms%20warrior%2C%20explained%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getflack.com%2Fp%2Fpalmer-dept-of-war%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Luckey%20thought%20the%20DoD%20sounded%20flaccid%20and%20vague%20and%20that%20the%20government%20should%20resurrect%20the%20pre-Cold%20War%20name%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20War.%20This%20would%20adequately%20state%20its%20purpose%3A%20to%20fight.%20The%20propagandist%20was%20looking%20for%2C%20as%20Meservey%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20more%20honest%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20War%20had%20a%20much%20better%20track%20record%20than%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20posted%20on%20X%20in%20August.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20rechristen%20the%20department.%20(Though%20formally%20changing%20the%20name%20requires%20an%20act%20of%20Congress.)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anduril%20Fury%20autonomous%20air%20vehicle%20on%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6810f7aba466d2b74ab47540%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Anduril%20Fury%20can%20reach%20speds%20of%20over%20650%20miles%20per%20hour%20and%20operate%20at%20altitudes%20of%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20feet.%3Cp%3EHollie%20Adams%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Luckey%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20in%20tech%20to%20throw%20his%20weight%20behind%20defense.%20While%20Anduril%20worked%20on%20one%20of%20its%20first%20major%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20equipping%20the%20southern%20border%20of%20the%20US%20with%20an%20AI-powered%2C%20virtual%20surveillance%20wall%20%E2%80%94%20employees%20at%20tech%20giants%20protested%20their%20companies'%20military%20contracts.%20In%202018%2C%20about%204%2C000%20Google%20workers%20signed%20a%20letter%20asking%20the%20company%20to%20cancel%20Project%20Maven%2C%20an%20intelligence-gathering%20Pentagon%20program%2C%20and%20to%20get%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employees-letter-urges-sundar-pichai-end-pentagon-ai-contract-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bthe%20business%20of%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Later%20that%20year%2C%20after%20the%20company%20did%20call%20it%20off%2C%20Luckey%20chastised%20Google%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20by%20a%20pretty%20radical%20fringe.%26quot%3B%20Anduril%20later%20won%20a%20Project%20Maven%20contract%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2Fanduril-industries-project-maven-palmer-luckey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Intercept%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%2C%20Luckey%20has%20repeatedly%20retold%20this%20story%20to%20cast%20himself%20as%20a%20fearless%20defender%20of%20freedom%2C%20a%20throwback%20to%20Cold%20War-era%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20when%20tech%20executives%20and%20Stanford%20academics%20courted%20the%20Pentagon.%20%26quot%3BIf%20both%20the%20smartest%20minds%20in%20technology%20abandoned%20defense%20innovation%2C%20the%20United%20States%20would%20forever%20lose%20its%20ability%20to%20protect%20our%20way%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20wrote%20in%20an%20essay%20for%20The%20Free%20Press%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20no%20one%20else%20was%20willing%20to%20solve%20that%20problem%2C%20I%20would.%26quot%3B%20He's%20also%20long%20maintained%20that%20those%20concerned%20with%20the%20morality%20of%20autonomous%20weapons%20should%20be%20the%20ones%20developing%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20moral%20high%20ground%20in%20outsourcing%20that%20work%20to%20people%20who%20are%20less%20ethical%20and%20less%20competent%20than%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Rogan%20earlier%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20rectitude%20has%20instilled%20in%20some%20tech%20bros%20the%20confidence%20to%20start%20their%20own%20chest-thumpingly%20patriotic%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPalmer%20is%20a%20guy%20who%20everyone%20in%20the%20defense%20tech%20ecosystem%20looks%20up%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Fil%20Aronshtein%2C%20who%20cofounded%20Dirac%2C%20an%20AI%20manufacturing%20company%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20inspired%20a%20lot%20of%20founders%20to%20be%20unapologetically%20themselves%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20fit%20into%20Silicon%20Valley's%20idea%20of%20a%20tech%20founder.%26quot%3B%20Where%20this%20stereotypical%20founder%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20shy%2C%20hunched-over%20nerd%20or%20laptop%20creature%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronshtein%20insists%20he%20isn't%20so%20ungainly.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20pro-American%2C%20and%20I'm%20proud%20of%20that.%20I%20lift%20weights.%20I%20can%20definitely%20be%20way%20more%20myself%20after%20seeing%20that%20Palmer%20can%20be%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he's%20most%20himself%2C%20Luckey%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20his%20disciples%20have%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Breal-life%20Tony%20Stark%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20is%20nerding%20out%20over%20anime%20and%20sci-fi.%20%26quot%3BScience%20fiction%20informs%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20in%20October.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20even%20so%20much%20that%20it%20predicted%20the%20future%20as%20it%20literally%20caused%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%20(Anduril%20is%20named%20after%20the%20%26quot%3BFlame%20of%20the%20West%26quot%3B%20sword%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lord%20of%20the%20Rings.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20bantering%20with%20the%20bros%20or%20cracking%20bawdy%20jokes%20on%20X.%20In%20December%2C%20when%20Anduril%20announced%20its%20autonomous%20submarines%20had%20traveled%20more%20mission%20miles%20than%20a%20lap%20around%20the%20Earth%2C%20Luckey%20quipped%20on%20the%20social%20media%20site%2C%20%26quot%3Balmost%20as%20far%20as%20the%20circumference%20of%20my%20post-holidays%20waistline!%26quot%3B%20Some%20of%20his%20shock%20jock%20takes%20could%20pass%20for%20those%20of%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20too%20many%20people%20who%20drink%20Starbucks%20and%20not%20enough%20who%20drink%20Mountain%20Dew%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20told%20Rogan.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20know%20exactly%20what%20I%20mean%20when%20I%20say%20that.%26quot%3B%20Some%20pro-natalist%20beliefs%20he%20espouses%20%E2%80%94%20that%20having%20fewer%20than%202.1%20children%20is%20treasonous%20%E2%80%94%20track%20the%20talking%20points%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKTmBoyle%2Fstatus%2F1755411965587980689%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20his%20serial-X-poster%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Silicon%20Valley%20elites%20going%20MAGA%20post%E2%80%94last%20year's%20election%2C%20Luckey%20is%20taking%20a%20Trump-stanning%20victory%20lap.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20true%20Trump%20OGs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Rogan.%20When%20Luckey%20was%2015%2C%20he%20wrote%20Trump%20a%20letter%20asking%20him%20to%20run%20for%20president%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20loved%20his%20extremist%20rhetoric%20going%20back%20to%202009!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20seems%20to%20stan%20Luckey%2C%20too%3A%20At%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20the%20president%20archly%20called%20Anduril's%20Roadrunner%20drone%20a%20%26quot%3Bnasty%20looking%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20tech%20industry%20stands%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20This%20month%2C%20Hegseth%20announced%20a%20plan%20to%20throw%20%241%20billion%20behind%20American%20drone%20manufacturing.%20In%20November%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20will%20acquire%20more%20off-the-shelf%20tech%20from%20companies%20that%20surge%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20speed%20of%20ingenuity.%26quot%3B%20That's%20a%20reversal%20from%20the%20government's%20decades%20of%20work%20with%20defense%20primes%20like%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Northrop%20Grumman%2C%20which%20have%20long%20depended%20on%20funding%20from%20lengthy%20contracts%20to%20make%20their%20products.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Army%20Secretary%20Dan%20Driscoll%20said%20on%20tech%20talk%20show%20TBPN%20that%20the%20death%20of%20one%20of%20those%20primes%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuccess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20Luckey's%20pitch%20all%20along%3B%20he%20told%20Rogan%20his%20goal%20at%20Anduril%20is%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20taxpayers%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20bills%20itself%20as%20the%20antithesis%20of%20a%20traditional%20defense%20prime.%20Instead%20of%20using%20government%20contracts%20to%20cover%20project%20expenses%2C%20Luckey's%20startup%20sells%20ready-made%20weapons%20to%20the%20government%20at%20a%20fixed%20price.%20To%20Shah%2C%20the%20defense%20tech%20investor%2C%20Anduril%20is%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20shift%20where%20we%20expect%20technology%20to%20move%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22833%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palmer%20Luckey%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20standing%20together%20and%20smiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838a7be6ffb6822ec61bf09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalmer%20Luckey%20(left)%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20(right)%3Cp%3EAnduril%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20is%20paying%20dividends.%20In%202024%2C%20Anduril's%20unmanned%20fighter%20jet%20Fury%20beat%20Boeing%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20and%20Northrop%20Grumman%20for%20the%20Air%20Force's%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%20program.%20The%20company%20is%20on%20a%20path%20to%20go%20public%20in%20%26quot%3Blow%20single-digit%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20told%20Bloomberg%20this%20fall.%20OpenAI%20is%20partnering%20with%20Anduril%20to%20build%20AI%20systems%20to%20thwart%20drone%20attacks.%20Even%20Luckey's%20old%20foe%20Meta%20is%20now%20working%20with%20Anduril%20on%20augmented%20reality%20wearables%20for%20the%20Army.%20The%20headsets%20turn%20warfighters%20into%2C%20as%20Luckey%20has%20written%2C%20%26quot%3Btechnomancers%26quot%3B%20who%20slay%20IRL%20opponents%20while%20peering%20at%20a%20screen%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjendarhy%2Fstatus%2F1978588915213705555%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooks%20straight%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BCall%20of%20Duty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20sound%20arrogant%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-meta-launch-eagleeye-military-wearables-ar-technology-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20collab%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I've%20got%20this%20shit%20figured%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20will%20Anduril's%20autonomous%20weapons%20work%20reliably%20in%20combat%3F%20Late%20last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fanduril-industries-defense-tech-problems-52b90cae%3Fgaa_at%3Deafs%26gaa_n%3DAWEtsqdZTCnvbSQIm9I95z_1SngrtGZFK57LFDfqxfGvd-JyQABjLE0skYNY7V0bHSU%253D%26gaa_ts%3D693269cd%26gaa_sig%3Dg2O9tNPlJYWgH8O9LugM7-9zilWKqAYdLsLJOoafqJM_9TqkfiS4rMpvAnR66Q4bYaCNxEWXJdcrJQJI3Owquw%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Faerospace-defense%2Fus-defense-firm-anduril-faces-setbacks-drone-crashes-2025-11-27%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20company's%20software%20platform%2C%20Lattice%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20suite%20of%20drone%20and%20counterdrone%20products%2C%20have%20been%20stymied%20by%20technical%20challenges%20and%20failed%20military%20tests.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is