Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkursk-ukraine-exploited-russias-dysfunctional-military-command-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eorganizational%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelousov%20said%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20had%20created%20five%20new%20divisions%2C%2013%20new%20brigades%2C%20and%2030%20new%20regiments%20in%202025.%20International%20think%20tanks%20estimate%20that%20Russian%20divisions%20can%20consist%20of%20between%2010%2C000%20and%2020%2C000%20troops%2C%20while%20regiments%20within%20typically%20have%20about%202%2C000%20soldiers%20and%20are%20further%20split%20into%20battalions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20cadets%20and%20officers%20prepare%20for%20the%20rehearsals%20of%20the%20Victory%20Day%20Red%20Square%20Parade%20in%20May%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69438d2304eda4732f2dbfad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussia's%20organizational%20structure%20includes%2030%20new%20regiments.%3Cp%3EContributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrigades%2C%20which%20typically%20exist%20as%20a%20separate%20formation%2C%20often%20have%20about%203%2C500%20to%204%2C500%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelousov%20said%20this%20new%20structure%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincluded%20a%20new%20division%2C%20called%20the%20Aerospace%20Forces%2C%20which%20has%20a%20regiment%20%26quot%3Bequipped%20with%20the%20unique%20S-500%20antiaircraft%20missile%20system%2C%20capable%20of%20striking%20targets%20in%20near%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20year%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20plans%20to%20add%20four%20more%20divisions%2C%2014%20brigades%2C%20and%2039%20new%20regiments%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20figures%20encompass%20formations%20that%20Russia%20has%20transformed%2C%20so%20they%20aren't%20necessarily%20an%20indicator%20of%20how%20widely%20Russia%20is%20expanding%20its%20military%20or